WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:09.000
Hi everyone, I'm Mihai Balashi, AWS user group leader from Budapest and part of the organizing team.

00:09.000 --> 00:16.000
While we're getting everything ready to roll, let me quickly walk you through how to get help today.

00:16.000 --> 00:22.000
Because knowing this will save you a lot of time once the game is live.

00:22.000 --> 00:28.000
First, have your builder ID ready and your browser updated.

00:28.000 --> 00:33.000
Sounds small, but it keeps you in the game if anything goes wrong.

00:33.000 --> 00:41.000
No builder ID yet? No rush. You have plenty of time, it's free and quick to set up.

00:41.000 --> 00:50.000
Once you're playing, feel free to use the hints. Some are free, no points lost and they can completely unblock you.

00:50.000 --> 00:59.000
Amazon Q developer is already set up in your environment. Use it like a teammate, not a last resort.

00:59.000 --> 01:05.000
And if you're still stuck, just raise your hand right there in the room.

01:05.000 --> 01:12.000
Your AWS user group leaders and AWS team members on site are right there to help you.

01:12.000 --> 01:17.000
Don't wait, don't struggle quietly. Ask early.

01:17.000 --> 01:24.000
Okay, that's all you need. Now get ready because things are about to get exciting.

01:24.000 --> 01:26.000
Back to you, Linda.

